I'm giving a talk about the
location side more tomorrow.

00:39:07.640 --> 00:39:11.150
There's the Maps API v2 talks
and the Floor Plans Tool for

00:39:11.150 --> 00:39:14.400
uploading as well as the Google
Maps Floor Plan Marker.

00:39:14.400 --> 00:39:15.010
Thank you very much.

